From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Steven <scrass@anaconda.com>
Date: Sun, 4 Aug 2025 22:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix tensorflow version from 2.18.0 to 2.18.1

Fix hardcoded tensorflow version in configure.sh to use 2.18.1 instead of 2.18.0
since tensorflow==2.18.0 does not exist on PyPI. This allows the build to proceed
without version resolution errors.
---
 oss_scripts/configure.sh | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/oss_scripts/configure.sh b/oss_scripts/configure.sh
index 0000000..1111111 100755
--- a/oss_scripts/configure.sh
+++ b/oss_scripts/configure.sh
@@ -41,7 +41,7 @@
   if [[ "$IS_NIGHTLY" == "nightly" ]]; then
     pip install tf-nightly
   else
-    pip install tensorflow==2.18.0
+    pip install tensorflow==2.18.1
   fi
 fi